            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-4">愿景</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 leading-relaxed text-sm">成为全球领先的AIGC技术平台，构建开放共享的AI生态，引领智能内容创作新时代。</p>
          </div>

          <!-- 理念卡片 -->
          <div class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-900 border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-800 p-8 hover:border-blue-500 transition-colors">
            <div class="w-16 h-16 mb-6 border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 flex items-center justify-center">
              <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-blue-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
